                                    <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> kumpt</add>.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <add>von
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>fürderl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> und <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sein wöllet durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz im dasselb alles, das im
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> also von dem
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <add><expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                            oheim</add>, geschickt ist <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>, on
